<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-margin-top-alt: auto; margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><b><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman';">Help the Podcast!&nbsp; </span></b><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman';">I would greatly appreciate it if you went to itunes, wrote a quick review and rated the show.&nbsp; This is a great way to increase downloads and to help the show grow.&nbsp; The more downloads, the more easily I can book high profile guests:&nbsp; <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/choice-conversations/id315666764">https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/choice-conversations/id315666764</a></span></p>
