</div> <!-- end postTitle -->
<div class="postBody">
	<img src ="http://assets.libsyn.com/content/2561488" class="postImage" >
	<p>A great conversation with the author/blogger Charles Hugh Smith who writes for the <a href="http://www.oftwominds.com/blog.html">OfTwoMinds</a> blog. We cover topics such as the financialization of our economy, the wealth and income gap, social and political subjects, and the various definitions of capitalism.</p>
<p>Although CHS and I weave in many topics into this episode we ran out of time to hear CHS's opinions on why we should be optimistic and hopeful of&nbsp;the future. That is why next week I will be inviting CHS back for another hour long discussion on Survival Preparation, Health, Diet, Organic Gardening, etc.. Should be another great chit-chat. Stay tuned.</p>
